  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate and compare the changes by two modalities: Imaging&#xD;
      by Strain by Speckle Tracking and Magnetic Resonance versus soluble markers of cardiac&#xD;
      dysfunction as early predictors of cardio-toxicity in cancer patients receiving low or high&#xD;
      doses of radiotherapy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
